doctordeathddracula.onmouseenter: function func3(q, b){ if (!q.parentNode.a){ q.parentNode.a = new Audio(); q.parentNode.a.src=d.music; q.parentNode.a.currentTime=1; } if(q.parentNode.a.ended){q.parentNode.a.currentTime=1;} q.parentNode.a.volume=0; q.parentNode.a.play(); if (q.parentNode.i){clearInterval(q.parentNode.i)} q.parentNode.i = setInterval(function(){ if(q.parentNode.a.volume >= 0.2){ clearInterval(q.parentNode.i); } q.parentNode.a.volume+=0.002; },20); }
